import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
col_names = []  # 
x_train2 = []  # 
count = 0  # dimension count
counts = []
accuracy = []  # adjusted-Rsquared

for idx in significant_variables.index:
    count += 1
    counts.append(count)
    col_names.append(idx)
    x_train2 = furnace_df[col_names]
    model = sm.OLS(y_train, x_train2).fit()  # 
    accuracy.append(model.rsquared_adj)  # adjusted-Rsqareaccuracy

for idx in furnace_df:
    if(idx in significant_variables.index or idx == 'grade'):
        pass
    else:
        count += 1
        counts.append(count)
        col_names.append(idx)
        x_train2 = furnace_df[col_names]
        model = sm.OLS(y_train, x_train2).fit()  # 
        accuracy.append(model.rsquared_adj)  # adjusted-Rsqareaccuracy

plt.xlabel("dimension (number of features)")
plt.ylabel("model pridiction accuracy")
plt.plot(counts, accuracy, '.-')

max_accuracy_id = accuracy.index(max(accuracy))+1
plt.plot([max_accuracy_id, max_accuracy_id], [min(accuracy), max(
    accuracy)], '--', color='red', label="fitness dimension")
plt.legend()

(4) 試問配適一個線性判別分析模型是否合適?若配適不佳，試說明其可能的原因為何?¶

from sklearn.discriminant_analysis import LinearDiscriminantAnalysis
from sklearn.model_selection import RepeatedStratifiedKFold
from sklearn.model_selection import cross_val_score
import numpy as np

# fit LDA model
LDAreg_KScatch = LinearDiscriminantAnalysis()
modelLDA_KScatch = LDAreg_KScatch.fit(X_train_KScatch, Y_train_KScatch)

LDAreg_Bumps = LinearDiscriminantAnalysis()
modelLDA_Bumps = LDAreg_Bumps.fit(X_train_Bumps, Y_train_Bumps)

# define method to evaluate model
cv = RepeatedStratifiedKFold(n_splits=15, n_repeats=5, random_state=59)

# evaluate model
KScatch_score = cross_val_score(
    modelLDA_KScatch, X_train_KScatch, Y_train_KScatch, scoring='accuracy', cv=cv, n_jobs=-1)
print("K_ScatchR2",np.mean(KScatch_score))

Bumps_score = cross_val_score(
    modelLDA_Bumps, X_train_Bumps, Y_train_Bumps, scoring='accuracy', cv=cv, n_jobs=-1)
print("BumpsR2",np.mean(Bumps_score))
